<HEAD>Bethlehem Steel And USW Begin Contract Talks</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PITTSBURGH (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Officials of Bethlehem Steel Corp. and the
United Steelworkers union began contract talks Thursday in an
effort to reach an early agreement on a 1989 labor pact.
   The two sides set April 21 as the target date for reaching an
